    "title": "Hurt, Insult, Threaten, Scream (HITS) Score",
    "desc": "The Hurt, Insult, Threaten, Scream (HITS) Score detects domestic abuse (intimate partner violence) in women and men in healthcare settings.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
            {
                "href": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9669164/",
                "text": "Sherin KM, Sinacore JM, Li XQ, Zitter RE, Shakil A. HITS: a short domestic violence screening tool for use in a family practice setting. Fam Med. 1998;30(7):508-512."
